string.name: cantOpenSimilarAccount
string.comment: Please note this string was simplified in January 2025. Before this, it used to state "You will not be allowed to open a new account with the same name, even if the case is different." Please update existing translations as required.

resources.string: ସମାନ ନାମ ସହିତ ଏକ ନୂଆ ଆକାଉଣ୍ଟ୍ ଖୋଲିବାକୁ ଆପଣଙ୍କୁ ଅନୁମତି ଦିଆଯିବ ନାହିଁ, ଯଦିଓ ନା‍ଁର କେସ୍ ଭିନ୍ନ ଥାଏ।
